# Per SPEC_V02B AC-5 + §5 risks: every `mmd bench` run materializes a full
# PWA + screenshots + logs per dream under runs/<run-id>/. That output can be
# tens or hundreds of megabytes and is reproducible from the dreams in
# bench/dreams/ — never commit it. The `runs/` directory is preserved as a
# placeholder so users can locate it without re-reading the README; only
# runs/README.md is tracked.
runs/*
!runs/README.md
